    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs beautifully\u2014perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you today. You\u2019re going to love how it handles, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
