    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, renowned for its eight individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. The powertrain is paired with a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical feedback. The chassis retains its precision with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and updated subframe bushings. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the replacement of rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring the dual-VANOS system and high-pressure oiling system remain in peak operating condition. The hydraulic steering rack offers the tactile transparency lost in newer electric systems, making this a superb choice for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Engine runs smooth. Regular maintenance records available. Interior is clean. Minor exterior blemishes. All systems functional.",
      "price": 32000.0,
